AND IT HAPPENED.

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.000
HE'S BEEN DOING IT
ALL ALONG,

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:54.000
AND I THINK THAT MAKES IT
A LOT EASIER

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.000
FOR THE TRANSITION
OF THE GIRLS.

