I'VE ONLY ADDED
 TO WHAT I WAS ALREADY DOING.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:07.000
I'M MUCH MORE
 INVOLVED IN THEIR LIFE.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.000
DADDY, HOW DO YOU
ROLL THE NAPKINS?

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:11.000
Brazelton:
 MARTY HAS A GAME PLAN.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:15.000
