 TEAM SPIRIT AT MY HOUSE.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:17.000
- Jedda: HELLO!
- HELLO.

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:21.000
PLAYING WITH EACH OTHER'S TOYS
 OR SHARING A SKIRT

