00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.000
Brazelton:
 THE RESULT:
 WONDERFUL GIRLS.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:29.000
- DADDY.
- YES.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.000
Amber:
 DAD DOES A LOT
 OF STUFF AROUND HERE.

