YOU KNOW,
"PICK UP YOUR COAT.
PUT YOUR SHOES AWAY.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.000
MAKE SURE YOUR BAG'S PUT AWAY.
DO YOUR HOMEWORK."

