YOU CAN ACTUALLY
POST YOUR ISSUES

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:05.000
AND SEE IF THERE'S
SOMETHING THAT YOU'VE
DONE WONDERFULLY.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:08.000
I THINK THE INTERNET CAN
 BE A VALUABLE RESOURCE

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:11.000
JUST TO SHARE EXPERIENCES 
AND TO SEE IF WE CAN LEARN
FROM EACH OTHER.

